text: Jaqueline Rodríguez or Diana Jaqueline Rodríguez Carrillo (born in Santiago Tequixquiac, 7 September 1996) is a Mexican professional footballer who plays as a defender for Liga MX Femenil side Guadalajara. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:People from Tequixquiac Category:Mexican footballers Category:Sportspeople from Mexico (state) Category:Mexican people of Portuguese-Jewish descent Category:Mexican people of Spanish descent
